cs.NE, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DS, cs.CE 

This paper is about optimization algorithms, specifically the performance of IPOP-saACM-ES on benchmark problems. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Other possible categories include cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), and cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science).
